
# 🎤 Voice Assistant using Python (Exercise)

## 📌 Objective
To develop a simple Voice Assistant application that can:
- Convert speech into text
- Convert text into speech
- Display output using a graphical interface

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies Used
- Python
- SpeechRecognition
- pyttsx3
- Tkinter

---

## ⚙️ Description

This project is a basic implementation of a Voice Assistant using Python.

The system performs the following steps:
1. Takes voice input from the user through a microphone
2. Converts speech into text using Google Speech Recognition API
3. Displays the text in a GUI window
4. Converts the same text into speech using pyttsx3

